text: Izimarino () is a rural locality (a village) in Tynbayevsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 312 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 46 km from Mishkino, 3 km from Tynbayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Izimarino
